[SHORT DESC]
Reduces Attack EVs by 10. Increases happiness.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>The Kelpsy Berry will make a Pokemon more friendly, but will also decrease its Attack stat by 10 EVs. If the holder uses the move Natural Gift, this Berry will provide a one-time 70 Base Power Fighting-type attack.</p>

<h2>Location</h2>
<p>Is available through the Dream World area Windswept Sky.</p>